  <amendments/>
  <summary date="2005-04-13T20:33:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Calls on Turkey to: (1) demonstrate that it is willing to abide by European Union (EU) laws; (2) eliminate all forms of discrimination, particularly those based on race or religion, and grant the Ecumenical Patriarch appropriate international recognition and ecclesiastic succession; and (3) safeguard religious and human rights.

Encourages Turkey to continue the advancement of processes and programs to modernize and democratize its own society.</summary>
